Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 30.06.24

Introduction

Welcome to Hiking! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our hiking trail app.

1. Information We Collect

1.1 Location Data

To provide you with accurate trail tracking and navigation, our App collects your location data in real-time while you are hiking. This data includes GPS coordinates and other location-related information.

1.2 Usage Data

We collect information about how you use our App, including the features you use, the trails you record, and the duration and frequency of your hiking activities. This data is collected anonymously and is not linked to any personal identifiers.

2. How We Use Your Information

2.1 Provide and Improve Our Services

We use your location data to record and display your hiking trails, provide real-time navigation, and enhance your overall hiking experience.

2.2 Safety and Security

Your information helps us maintain the safety and security of our App and services, including detecting and preventing fraud or unauthorized activities.

3. Sharing Your Information

We do not share your information with any third parties. Your data is used solely for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy.

4. Data Retention

We retain your location data for as long as necessary to provide our services and fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. You can request deletion of your data by contacting us at ohangor@gmail.com.

5. Your Rights

You have the right to access, correct, or delete your location data. You can also object to the processing of your data or request data portability. To exercise these rights, please contact us at ohangor@gmail.com.

6. Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on our App and updating the "Effective Date" above.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

ohangor@gmail.com

Conclusion

By using our App, you agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting with your hiking adventures!
